Package eu.cqse.check.cpp.misra.preprocessor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ForbiddenSequencesInIncludeCheck
    Checks that included header names do not contain forbidden sequences.
    IncludeDirectivesShouldNotBePreceededByCodeCheck
    Checks that include statements are not preceded by code (Misra 20.1)
    IncludeFilenameDelimiterCheck
    Checks that all includes use '<...>' or '\"...\"' as delimiter for header names.
    MacroArgumentWithDirectivesCheck
    Checks if a macro is called with arguments, which contain tokens looking like preprocessor directives.
    PreprocessorDirectiveEndCheck
    Checks if the sequence of preprocessor directives is valid per-file.
    PreprocessorDirectiveLineStartCheck
    Checks if every line starting with '#' as token is a valid preprocessing directive.
    PreprocessorDirectiveUtils
    Implements utility functions for handling preprocessor directives
